    "The creativity and human touch that go into producing topnotch lesson plans and instructional resources cannot be entirely replicated by AI systems.",
    "Works for Detection ChatGPT-based Texts and Other PrecautionsResearchers explore the zero-shot machine-generated text identification problem, in which they employ various probabilities computed by a generative model to ascertain whether a candidate passage was sampled from it.",
